    • Constructor Detail

      • DynamicAuthTempl

        public DynamicAuthTempl(int pop_type,
                byte[] data)
        Constructor for DynamicAuthTempl. All Authentication attempts are initiated off-card, and occur based on the authentication scenerio. This may include authentication to the card with the PIV Admin key to manage the PIV application data. This may also include requesting authentication from the card too ensure there is a corresponding private key for a certificate on the card, such as PIV or CAK Authentication.
        Parameters:
        pop_type - int
        data - byte[]
